# Historical database - KX Delta Platform

Original URL: https://code.kx.com/platform/stream/dw_historical_db/

# Historical database

The Historical Database (_HDB_) is used to access all on-disk historical data.
Generally this will be data that was captured prior to the current day.

[![Screenshot](../img/serviceclass/hdb_name.jpg)](../img/serviceclass/hdb_name.jpg
"click to expand")

parameter | value  
---|---  
Directory | ENV=DELTADATA_HOME=/KxWarehouseData/hdblog

